first:
Sudo apt-get intall elinks
Sudo apt install curl

then:

git clone https://github.com/sardach/rae-cli/
cd rae-cli
sudo install -Dm755 "rae" "/usr/bin/rae"


run it;

rae-cli

rae -td mundo

will provide all the defintions of the word 'mundo'

rae -c saber

will provide all the conjugations of the verb 'saber'
